There&#39;s a known bug in javac about statically importing generated methods. javac concludes that an annotation processor can&#39;t &#39;fix&#39; it incorrectly and just throws out an error.

The fix is to not statically import it:

    import com.business.lunch.dto.OfferContent;

    ....
        return OfferContent.builder();

